OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a cloudier day, with
OL,6,Fsome outbreaks of rain, this mostly
OL,7,Flight but perhaps a few heavier
OL,8,Foutbreaks developing over Lanarkshire.
OL,9,FWest coast perhaps brightening up
OL,10,Flater. Rather humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA few showers continuing this
OL,13,Fevening in the east, but skies will be
OL,14,Fclearing from the west and the night
OL,15,Fwill be dry with some clear spells,
OL,16,Flocalised low cloud.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FLow cloud burning off then a
OL,19,Fdry bright day with some sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
