OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday will be sunny and very warm.
OL,7,FSunny, hot Thursday, perhaps some
OL,8,Fthundery showers later. Showery on
OL,9,FFriday, less warm.
